ents \")], -1 /* CACHED */)), _cache[2] || (_cache[2] = _createElementVNode(\"p\", {\n    class: \"text-lg mb-8 opacity-90 leading-relaxed\"\n  }, [_createTextVNode(\" From Confused to Confident \"), _createElementVNode(\"br\"), _createTextVNode(\" Get started with a free trial today! \")], -1 /* CACHED */)), _createVNode(_component_router_link, {\n    to: \"/login\"\n  }, {\n    default: _withCtx(() => _cache[0] || (_cache[0] = [_createElementVNode(\"button\", {\n      class: \"cta-button pulse-animation\"\n    }, \" Get Started \", -1 /* CACHED */)])),\n    _: 1 /* STABLE */,\n    __: [0]\n  })]), _createCommentVNode(\" App Preview \"), _cache[3] || (_cache[3] = _createStaticVNode(\"<div class=\\\"relative fade-in-right\\\" data-v-fae5bece><div class=\\\"bg-white rounded-xl overflow-hidden shadow-2xl transform perspective-1000 rotate-y-[-5deg] rotate-x-[5deg] floating-animation hover:rotate-y-[-2deg] hover:rotate-x-[2deg] hover:scale-105 transition-all duration-300\\\" data-v-fae5bece><div class=\\\"bg-gray-100 px-4 py-3 border-b border-gray-200\\\" data-v-fae5bece><div class=\\\"flex gap-2\\\" data-v-fae5bece><span class=\\\"w-3 h-3 bg-red-500 rounded-full\\\" data-v-fae5bece></span><span class=\\\"w-3 h-3 bg-yellow-500 rounded-full\\\" data-v-fae5bece></span><span class=\\\"w-3 h-3 bg-green-500 rounded-full\\\" data-v-fae5bece></span></div></div><div class=\\\"h-80 bg-gray-50 flex\\\" data-v-fae5bece><div class=\\\"w-64 bg-indigo-600 text-white p-6\\\" data-v-fae5bece><div class=\\\"flex items-center gap-2 text-xl font-bold mb-4\\\" data-v-fae5bece><span class=\\\"text-2xl\\\" data-v-fae5bece>📚</span><span data-v-fae5bece>Stardy</span></div><div class=\\\"text-lg mb-1\\\" data-v-fae5bece>Hi, James!</div><div class=\\\"text-sm opacity-80\\\" data-v-fae5bece>Let&#39;s study and finish your goals!</div></div><div class=\\\"flex-1 p-4\\\" data-v-fae5bece><div class=\\\"flex justify-between items-center\\\" data-v-fae5bece><div class=\\\"flex gap-4\\\" data-v-fae5bec